{
  "stem": "2581.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was our shield.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was our-- it was father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "When he laid down at back home or took a rest after dinner-- then we had early dinner, like 2 o'clock-- and customers could come in and a customer was important.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "No one would wake my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This is the kind of respect we gave him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And my father, like I mentioned before, had problems with his stomach so he went to these spas.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And when we came into the ghetto, my father said, I never felt so good.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I now know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That fat was used up, but after three months that fat was missing, and he started to get those boils on his neck that-- I remember, for the rest of the time that we were together, he had constant boils and it was bandaged and all that.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did the best how I could to take care of my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember, when we used to get a bread for the week-- each person.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father, he would cut up in the evening this bread into four pieces because it was for-- we had two breads, right?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when we cut up the pieces, my father would say, you see my child?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This piece is uneven.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let's even it out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he would even it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For me a piece, for him a piece.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By the time it remained for the next day to live on, there wasn't much left because we kept evening it out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The hunger was beyond description, and we lived like that in the ghetto for about-- let's see, from '42 to '44.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No pleasures, no relaxation.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
